  "subject": "Migrate so-cnfm-lcm from Flyway to Liquibase",
  "commit_message": "Migrate so-cnfm-lcm from Flyway to Liquibase\n\nFlyway 8.5.13 does not support MariaDB 11.7, causing the\nso-cnfm-lcm pod to crashloop on startup. Replace Flyway with\nLiquibase (matching the migration already done in the parent\nSO repo) and add a DataBaseServiceIntegrationTest that boots\nthe full Spring context with Liquibase migrations enabled and\nvalidates CRUD on all tables.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4372\nChange-Id: I3a1a289aa8c295fc05996d612a5f99916ddfe1f4\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
